description: This file defines a Java interface named JavaEvent used for IPC communication, extending ObjectIPC, and containing a multicast group constant.

classes.name: JavaEvent
classes.description: An interface indicating that events are produced by Java-based services, marshaling content via ObjectIPC, and supporting multicast messaging.

methods.name: IC_EVENT_MULTICAST_GROUP
methods.description: A constant string defining the multicast group IP address for events.
